games.comment: Torrey Smith. It was pretty cool to see Smith's first 3 career catches go for scores. Unfortunately, Smith, who finished with 5 grabs for 152 yards, suffered a hamstring injury in the second half and limped off the field. Stay tuned for details. If Smith is OK, he's definitely worth adding to your fantasy roster.
